P=(\pi)
M \cong R^{N_0} \oplus (R/P)^{N_1}\oplus\dots
M_i=\pi^iM \cong(P^i)^{N_0}\oplus(P^i/P^{i+1})^{N_{i+1}}\oplus(P^i/P^{i+2})^{N_{i+2}}\oplus\dots
i
M_i/M_{i+1}\cong (P^i/P^{i+1})^{N_0}\oplus(P^i/P^{i+1})^{N_{i+1}}\oplus(P^i/P^{i+1})^{N_{i+2}}\oplus\dots
\text{dim}_{R/P}(P^i/P^{i+1})=1
n_i=\text{dim}_{R/P}(M_i/M_{i+1})=N_0+\sum_{\nu>i}N_i
